* FILENAME:         NE68133.CIR
* NEC PART NUMBER:  NE68133
* LAST MODIFIED:    7/97
* BIAS CONDITIONS:  Vce=1V to 8V, Ic=1mA to 30mA
* FREQ RANGE:       0.1GHz to 8GHz
*
*                            CCBpkg
*                    .-------||--------.  
*                    |          CCB    |   
*                    |      .--||---.  |       COLLECTOR
* BASE               |      |        | |             
*                    |      |   /----o-o-----o--Lcx--o  
*            o--Lbx--o-LB---o--|Q1   |       |       
*                    |      B   \   --       --      
*                    |          |   -- CCE   -- CCEpkg
*                    --CBEpkg E o----'       |           
*                    --         |            |      
*                    |         LE            |       
*                    `----------o------------'       
*                               |                   
*                               Lex            
*                               |  
*                               o EMITTER
*                                
*       CCB    = 0.07pF          LB  = 0.9nH             
*       CCE    = 0.01pF          LE  = 1.2nH           
*       CCBpkg = 0.2pF           Lbx = 0.3nH          
*       CCEpkg = 0.2pF           Lcx = 0.6nH             
*       CBEpkg = 0.01pF          Lex = 0.3nH          
*
*                   c b e
.SUBCKT NE68133/CEL 2 1 3
Q1  5 7 8 NE68100
CCB 7 5 0.07E-12
CCE 5 8 0.01E-12
LE  8 6 1.2E-9
LB  4 7 0.9E-9
CCBPKG 4 5 0.2E-12
CCEPKG 5 6 0.2E-12
CBEPKG 4 6 0.01E-12
LBX 1 4 0.3E-9
LCX 5 2 0.6E-9
LEX 6 3 0.3E-9
.MODEL NE68100 NPN 
+( IS=2.7e-16    BF=185           NF=1.02        VAF=15           IKF=0.055
+ ISE=1.77e-11   NE=2.1           BR=1           NR=1             VAR=0  
+ IKR=0          ISC=0            NC=2           RE=0.6           RB=12  
+ RBM=3.7        IRB=1.2e-5       RC=8           CJE=1.2e-12      VJE=0.77 
+ MJE=0.5        CJC=0.8e-12      VJC=0.27       MJC=0.56         XCJC=0  
+ CJS=0          VJS=0.75         MJS=0          FC=0.5           TF=14e-12
+ XTF=3          VTF=25           ITF=0.1        PTF=0            TR=0.3e-9
+ EG=1.11        XTB=0            XTI=3          KF=0             AF=1 )
*
* NOTE:  CEL develops models using the Libra simulator.  For this simulator, 
*        a value of 0 for VAR and IKR is interpreted as infinity.
.ENDS
*$

